Hardware:
    stm32 modi board and jlink v8
desktop:
    archlinux installed in virutalbox on a winxp host
software:
    pacman -S openocd arm-none-eabi-gcc arm-none-eabi-binutils arm-none-eabi-gdb minicom git
    libopencm3(please refer to www.github.com/libopencm3)

code(uses libopencm3 library) port to my modi stm32 board bought from taobao
in each sub directory, run 'make all' to build the target elf file,
run 'make V=1 flash' to flash the elf file to target board through jlink.

